data.description: This Hampshire Model was built in 2019 by Lennar. It has 5 bedrooms, (1 on the main level); 3-Full Baths, finished 2-car garage, loft on the upper level along with the other 4 bedrooms.  Kitchen has 42" cabinets, and both kitchen & baths have 'comfort counter heights'. The family room, which includes a Gas-log fireplace, with the wall of windows allows you to enjoy the beautiful pond view out the back of the home. The main level bedroom & full bath makes this perfect for office or fitness use.  Plenty of storage areas.  Laundry room on upper level. Definitely a home that is ready to meet your lifestyle needs. NEW INFO -  SELLER IS OFFERING UP TO A $5,000.00 DOLLAR SELLER CONCESSION - use to buy down your interest rate; towards your down payment; or towards paying your closing costs/fees - with a full price offer.
